👉 Agar false → skip ho jayega


2. if-else (Dono taraf handle karo)
Agar condition true → ek kaam
False → dusra kaam
Example :

let marks = 35;

if (marks >= 40) {
  console.log("Pass ho gaya! 🎉");
} else {
  console.log("Fail ho gaya 😔, padhai karo");
}



3-else-if(Aur check karo)👉
 Jab multiple conditions check karni ho
👉 Aur sirf ek hi block execute karna ho


Example :-
let marks = 75;

if (marks >= 90) {
  console.log("Grade A");
} 
else if (marks >= 75) {
  console.log("Grade B");
} 
else {
  console.log("Fail");
}



