for in Loop :-
for...in → keys / property names pe iterate karta hai
Yeh mainly plain objects ({}) ke liye banaya gaya hai.
Kya karta hai?

Key / Index deta hai

👉 Kaha use hota hai?

Mostly Object ke liye

Array me bhi use hota hai (par recommended nahi)

👉 Kab use kare?

Jab object ke keys chahiye


Example (Object):-
let user = {
  name: "Harshu",
  age: 22
};

for (let key in user) {
  console.log(key);        // name, age
  console.log(user[key]);  // Harshu, 22
}

